<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-4">Pertanyaan yang Sering Diajukan</h2>
    <p class="text-center text-gray-600 mb-12">Temukan jawaban untuk pertanyaan umum</p>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <details class="bg-orange-50 rounded-lg p-6 group">
        <summary class="font-semibold cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
          <span>Apakah saya bisa mencoba gratis terlebih dahulu?</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 transform group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">Ya, kami menyediakan free trial selama 14 hari tanpa perlu kartu kredit. Anda bisa mencoba semua fitur Business plan secara gratis.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="bg-orange-50 rounded-lg p-6 group">
        <summary class="font-semibold cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
          <span>Apakah data saya aman?</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 transform group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">Sangat aman! Kami menggunakan enkripsi SSL dan backup data otomatis setiap hari. Data Anda tersimpan di server yang aman dan terpercaya.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="bg-orange-50 rounded-lg p-6 group">
        <summary class="font-semibold cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
          <span>Bagaimana cara upgrade atau downgrade paket?</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 transform group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">Anda bisa upgrade atau downgrade paket kapan saja dari dashboard. Perubahan akan berlaku di periode billing berikutnya.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="bg-orange-50 rounded-lg p-6 group">
        <summary class="font-semibold cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
          <span>Apakah tersedia training untuk tim saya?</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 transform group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">Ya, kami menyediakan video tutorial, dokumentasi lengkap, dan untuk paket Enterprise tersedia training online bersama tim kami.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="bg-orange-50 rounded-lg p-6 group">
        <summary class="font-semibold cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
          <span>Apakah bisa integrasi dengan sistem lain?</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 transform group-open:rotate-180 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">Tentu! Kami support integrasi dengan berbagai payment gateway, e-commerce platform, dan accounting software.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
